OL,3,CAir Ambulance Charity says fuel costs
OL,4,Chave risen by #25,000 a month
OL,6,FKent Surrey Sussex Air Ambulance is
OL,7,Ffacing extra costs of #25,000 a month,
OL,8,Fdue to a 63% increase in the cost of
OL,9,Faviation fuel.
OL,11,FThe charity (KSS) says the dramatic
OL,12,Frise in prices have come since the
OL,13,Fbeginning of the Middle East conflict.
OL,14,FIt means the cost of operating it's
OL,15,Fhelicopters is putting even more
OL,16,Fpressure on its financial
OL,17,Fsustainability.
OL,19,FKSS chief executive David Welch said:
OL,20,F""As a charity, and the only air
OL,21,Fambulance for the South East of
OL,26,@|D@BOU
