OL,3,CAir Ambulance Charity says fuel costs
OL,4,Chave risen by #25,000 a month
OL,6,FEngland, we're growing increasingly
OL,7,Fconcerned at the continued significant
OL,8,Fincrease in the cost of aviation
OL,10,Ffuel which presents a huge challenge
OL,11,Ffor us financially. While we have
OL,12,Fmitigation plans in place, the
OL,13,Funprecedented 63% rise in the cost of
OL,14,Faviation fuel means that we now need
OL,15,Fto raise even more funding from within
OL,16,Four communities, where so many people
OL,17,Fare also facing an increasingly
OL,18,Fdifficult financial climate, to help
OL,19,Fkeep us flying."
