OL,3,CAir Ambulance Charity says fuel costs
OL,4,Chave risen by #25,000 a month
OL,6,FHe goes on to say: "Our helicopters
OL,7,Fare a genuine lifeline for people
OL,8,Fwithin our communities and that's why
OL,9,Fwe want to ensurewe can be here for
OL,10,Fthe millions of people living,
OL,11,Fworking, visiting or travelling
OL,12,Fthrough the South East, ready to
OL,13,Frespond and ensure the best possible
OL,14,Fpatient outcomes when the very worst
OL,15,Fhappens. Every lifesaving mission we
OL,16,Fmake is almost entirely funded by the
OL,17,Fkindness and generosity of our
OL,18,Fcommunities. That's why ongoing and
OL,19,Fincreased public support for KSS
OL,20,Fduring these challenging times is more
OL,21,Fvital than ever in helping us to reach
OL,22,Fpatients and save lives."
